results.title: Cowboy One
results.description: The cowboy boot is a classic American footwear style that originated in the Wild West. These boots are designed to withstand the rugged conditions of ranch life and horseback riding, and have become a popular fashion statement across the country.

results.title: Classic Black
results.description: A classic black social shoe is a timeless dress shoe that is a staple in any formal or semi-formal wardrobe. Typically made from high-quality leather or suede, these shoes are designed to be sleek, sophisticated, and versatile.

results.title: Yellow Boom
results.description: A yellow leather boot is a bold and stylish footwear choice that can add a pop of color to any outfit. There are many different styles of yellow leather boots available, from classic work boots to fashion-forward ankle boots.

results.title: Classic Two Tones
results.description: A two-toned leather boot is a unique and stylish footwear choice that can add a touch of sophistication to any outfit. These boots typically feature two different shades of leather or suede, often in contrasting colors or textures, creating a distinctive and eye-catching look.
